    Project|Save snapshot...                  @{b}Amiga-S@{ub}
    Project|Save TVC...                       @{b}Amiga-\\@{ub}
    Project|Save as SpriteMakerEA project...  (none)
    Project|Save as TextMakerEA project...    (none)
    Project|Save screenshot as IFF ACBM...    (none)
    Project|Save screenshot as IFF ILBM...    @{b}Amiga-_@{ub}
    Project|Save screenshot as BMP...         (none)
    Project|Quicksave snapshot                @{b}Amiga-5@{ub}
    Project|Audit games                       @{b}Amiga-J@{ub}
    Project|Act as server                     (none)
    Project|Connect as client...              (none)
